            <title>[GROOVY-1030] no source and line number is shown in exceptions thrown from inside a script</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-1030</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;consider the script:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;throw new Exception(&quot;foo&quot;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;the stack trace should show  the line number and script name of the script which has thrown this exception. Instead the trace shows something like &quot;unknown source&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
